{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"daac39842a","title":"同意迅速包围南口昌平唐山等敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"659b640c7d","index":0,"year":1948,"month":12,"day":12,"articleId":"daac39842a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"919da50ab9","type":"paragraph","text":"同意迅速包围南口昌平唐山等敌”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"daac39842a"},{"id":"48ac692db9","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年12月12日）林、罗、刘并程、黄各电均悉。（一）同意迅速包围南口、昌平之敌，包国时注意以主力位于南口、北平间，只以一小部攻占八达岭。（二）同意迅速包围唐山、芦台之敌，如芦台敌已撒至塘活，则包围塘活。（三）新保安确为三十五军两个师，三十五军之另一个师在北平，程黄全力可用于包围南口、昌平。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"daac39842a"},{"id":"9c4870aaab","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"daac39842a"},{"id":"5d92a9c6e0","type":"paragraph","text":"十二日十八时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给东北野战军司令员林能、政治[2]程、黄，指程子华、黄志勇，当时分别任东北野战军第二兵团司令员和参谋长。[3]八达岭，长裁关胜，位于北京市延庆县南部。4]八达岭，长裁关胜，位于北京市延庆县南部。15八达岭，长裁关胜，位于北京市延庆县南部。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"daac39842a"}],"page":{"id":"5a4782a3b2","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"daac39842a","start":381,"end":381}}}},"__N_SSG":true}